description:
Dillo 3.2 open-source web browser is now available for download with SVG support for math formulas, support for WebP images, and more. Here's what's new!

The post Dillo 3.2 Open-Source Web Browser Released to Celebrate 25th Anniversary appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: Dillo 3.2 Open-Source Web Browser Released to Celebrate 25th Anniversary
